<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Sun, 20 Feb 2022 12:52:29 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>買車送 PS5  Toyota 限量版 Yaris GR Sport GT7 新車</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/20/yaris-gr-sport-gt7/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=yaris-gr-sport-gt7</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 20 Feb 2022 12:52:11 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087082</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Toyota 特別為 Gran Turismo 7（跑車浪漫旅 7）推出一款 Yaris 限量版車款，這款車將會 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Toyota 特別為 Gran Turismo 7（跑車浪漫旅 7）推出一款 Yaris 限量版車款，這款車將會在遊戲中出現，而限量只有 100 部。而購買這款限量版汽車，將附送 PlayStation 5 遊戲機一部以及 GT7 遊戲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/articleimage_1075618.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1087083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/articleimage_1075618-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/articleimage_1075618-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/articleimage_1075618.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmqSZosLRw52P1dHQyA.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1087084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmqSZosLRw52P1dHQyA-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmqSZosLRw52P1dHQyA-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmqSZosLRw52P1dHQyA-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmqSZosLRw52P1dHQyA.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmc_UzJqgkaKP1dHQyA.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1087085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmc_UzJqgkaKP1dHQyA-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmc_UzJqgkaKP1dHQyA-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmc_UzJqgkaKP1dHQyA-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/l52R0ZSgmc_UzJqgkaKP1dHQyA.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Toyota Yaris GR Sport GT7 Edition 將會同 GT7 遊戲一樣，在 2022 年 3 月 4 日上市。買車將會附隨 PlayStation 5 遊戲主機以及 Gran Turismo 7 遊戲。新車將會以 Yaris GR Sport Electic Hybrid 作為基礎，並在前葉子板上將會有 GT 遊戲標誌。</p><p>PlayStation 也跟 Toyota 合作，成為西班牙 Toyota Gazoo Racing Iberian Cup 比賽的主要贊助商。而想買 GT7 送車，就要參加西班牙當地的 Spanish Gran Turismo Championship 電競比賽，冠軍車手可獲得這部 Yaris GR Sport GT7 Edition 一部。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://traxion.gg/limited-edition-toyota-yaris-gran-turismo-7-includes-a-ps5-partnership-extended/">traxion</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
