</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Android 13 新增電話串流畫面功能  Windows、macOS、Linux 實時顯示手機畫面</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/19/android-13-pixel/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=android-13-pixel</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 06:00:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Android 13]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[PIXEL]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086427</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google 為 Pixel 電話用戶提供全新功能，供用戶將電話上的畫面直播串流至電腦螢幕上，以擴大 Andr [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Google 為 Pixel 電話用戶提供全新功能，供用戶將電話上的畫面直播串流至電腦螢幕上，以擴大 Android 電話的串連性。</p><p>報道指，Android 13 將以瀏覽器的網頁模擬器，把電話應用程式中的畫面內容「直播串流」至電腦螢幕上，為用家提供遠距連線功能。而每個應用程式會在串流時分立成獨立的視窗畫面，可以自由點擊、拖動及輸入內容。當用家想切換應用程式時，只需按下左下角的菜單，便能盡覽電話上的應用程式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58-694x386.png" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58-694x386.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58-1280x711.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58-768x427.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.58.png 1468w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： Google</p><p>Google 將有關功能開放予所有應用程式，用家只需在啟動「直播串流」功能後便能操作電話，而電話的通知亦會於電腦螢幕上顯示。不論是 Windows PC、macOS，抑或是 Linux 用戶亦能使用該功能，擴大 Android 電話的串連性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086456" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37-694x432.png" alt="" width="694" height="432" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37-694x432.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37-1280x797.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37-768x478.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/螢幕截圖-2022-02-15-下午 7.00.37.png 1468w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：9to5Google</p><p>Google 更為旗下 ChromeOS 用戶提供更多元化的功能，用戶可於指定的應用程式中直播串流，亦無需在瀏覽器中操作。不過報道指，上述功能仍處於測試階段，未能如網頁版的「直播串流」般成熟穩定。</p><p>「直播串流」功能暫只支援 Google Pixel 電話，預計於今年年底正底推出，未有透露未來會否應用至其他電話中。</p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/2/14/22933951/google-android-13-pixel-streaming-apps-notifications-chromebook-pc">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=6ZtZ3AJoCj8:pB_NwzYHQcA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=6ZtZ3AJoCj8:pB_NwzYHQcA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>整合多個 Windows 11 新功能 Amazon Appstore＋共享視窗＋新 Media Player</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/19/windows-11-amazon-apps-media-player/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=windows-11-amazon-apps-media-player</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 19 Feb 2022 05:58:59 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[microsoft]]></category><category><![CDATA[windows 11]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1086661</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Windows 11 於推出後迎來首次大更新，提供 Amazon Appstore、共享視窗、更新 Media [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Windows 11 於推出後迎來首次大更新，提供 Amazon Appstore、共享視窗、更新 Media Player 與記事本等多個功能。</p><p>是次 Windows 11 更新版本包含多項新功能，與以往主動下載的每月更新有別，用家需從選按「獲取更新」方會下載。當中的新功能包括：</p><p>加入 Amazon Appstore</p><p>工具列加入天氣應用</p><p>工具列可直接靜音 / 取消靜音 Teams 的麥克風</p><p>透過工具列就能在 Teams 共享視窗</p><p>第二個螢幕也會顯示時鐘與日期</p><p>新版 Media Player 與記事本</p><p>加入 Amazon Appstore：</p><p>Windows Subsystem for Android 功能會為 Windows 11 裝置安裝 Android 作業系統，令 Windows 11 裝置亦可使用 Android 提供的應用程式。而是次更新則為 Windows 11 加入 Amazon Appstore，預計會為用戶提供至少 1000 個應用程式，一改以往應用程式貧乏的缺點。新功能暫只支援美國用戶，用戶可使用  Amazon Appstore 下載 Kindle 及 Lords Mobile 等多個 Android 應用程式。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_84471"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K6SpHPF40Ik?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>工具列加入天氣應用：</p><p>於左下方的小元件面板中加入天氣圖標，把鼠標移到圖標上便可查看天氣資料，為用戶提供更方便、快速的查看資訊功能。把鼠標移開後天氣欄便會關閉，想持續查看天氣欄只需連擊天氣圖標便可。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_44096"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xbcbFW9qwdo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>可於工作列切換咪高峰至靜音或取消靜音：</p><p>於 Teams 通話時，用戶可按右下方的咪高峰圖示，選擇把咪高峰調至靜音或取消靜音。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_31656"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0ezWXLDa1aI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>在 Teams 中共享視窗：</p><p>Windows 11 於 Teams 中加入共享視窗功能，令用戶可於使用 Teams 時共享指定視窗，用戶只需於程式縮圖上點選分享，便可便用共享螢幕功能。當中止共享時，只需點選「停止共用」便可，而「共用此視窗」則可切換共享的視窗。官方指正確使用上述功能可減少中斷會議的可能性。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_59538"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ci-b8Y_gA0E?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>於第二個螢幕顯示時鐘與日期：</p><p>會於第二螢幕新增時鐘與日期，方便用戶隨時查看。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/External_Desktop_Clock-1024x683-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1086662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/External_Desktop_Clock-1024x683-1-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/External_Desktop_Clock-1024x683-1-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/External_Desktop_Clock-1024x683-1-768x512.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/External_Desktop_Clock-1024x683-1.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源： Microsoft</p><p>更新 Media Player 與記事本（於 Microsoft Store 更新）：</p><p>Media Player 將取代 Groove Music，而 Groove Music 的資料庫和播放清單會自動轉移至 Media Player，用戶可快速瀏覽和播放音樂，更能創建、管理播放清單，亦會自動整合電腦的媒體內容。除了加入新功能外，Media Player 及記事本將使用全新介面設計，提供深色模式選擇。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_62273"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nG5CNcDyFa8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://blogs.windows.com/windowsexperience/2022/02/15/bringing-you-closer-to-what-you-love-with-new-experiences-in-windows-11/">Microsoft</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
